                        <button data-quiz-type="concepts" class="quiz-tab flex-1 whitespace-nowrap py-4 px-1 border-b-2 font-medium text-sm border-transparent text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700 hover:border-gray-300">Quiz Istruzioni Operative MSB</button>
